{"tid":1158153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女人可以變得咁快","createTime":"2019-05-16T18:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T09:34:52.000Z","uid":198087,"like":75,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"283b77232e90c4248d47f2006cd2647e82dace2c","tid":1158153,"uid":198087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T18:33:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我同個ex係地下情<br />\n同佢一齊三年幾今年一月尾分咗手<br />\n分手原因係因為佢唔知自己仲中唔中意我仲有唔想拍拖想自由<br />\n拍拖個時到第二年已經幾乎零身體接觸但係佢個時話自己中意我<br />\n拍拖個時即使佢啲friend 問佢佢都唔會承認同我一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排有個friend見到佢同條新仔拖住手返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我同佢啲 friend 講起先知佢同條仔一齊咗一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己已經放低咗佢點解要比我知依啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來我係真係只係一廂情願起佢心目中咁微不足道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪算比人帽咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主正柒頭做咗馬明都唔知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我中意你中意我咋 一直當你係兵咋<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c02dac935b9598fe60c415f087a0eb0f138aa268","tid":1158153,"uid":201480,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T18:40:11.000Z","msg":"佢冇唔中意你 只係唔夠中意你姐"},{"pid":"1f9342edf9bca8ee187f730b2ad7e4e4a636c7b5","tid":1158153,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T18:48:39.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"0990ef228ffb5b93b03013768a2802078a0044da","tid":1158153,"uid":252901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T20:01:29.000Z","msg":"好地地又點會同你地下情<br />\n仲要同其他人一齊，而啲朋友又知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n努力收拾心情啦！<br />